Here are the 2nd and 3rd verses:

He paid the debt on Calvary
He saved my soul and set me free;
I'm glad that Jesus did all my sins erase.
And now I sing a brand new song
Amazing grace the whole day long;
Christ Jesus paid the debt that I could never pay.

Someday He's coming back for me;
I'll live with Him eternally.
Won't it be glory to see Him on that day?
And then I'll sing a brand new song
Amazing grace the whole day long;
Christ Jesus paid the debt that I could never pay.
